    "To enable readers to obtain a deeper and more comprehensive understanding of temporal action detection, Sects.",
    "5 and 6 introduce temporal action detection in horizontal and vertical ways, from the design method to the learning method, using two different research routes to make the structure of the paper more rigorous.",
    "Sections 7 and 8 present conclusions and prospects.",
    "Figure 2 shows the structure diagram of the article.",
    "This section introduces some relevant information in respect of temporal action detection."
